            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Determined from cross section for production of 26Al",
                " ground state via 417-keV transition measured at 90",
                " degrees and relative angular distributions measured",
                " at 5.5, 10.0 and 14.0 MeV.",
                "Sum of the contribution to ground state production",
                " from other gamma rays is observed to be < 10%, even",
                " at higher energies."
